text = "Eye witnesses stated that Colt was last seen on DIT lobby. Prior to his disappearance,
he was seen with four other peaople, who parted ways with him at exactly 6pm due to unknown
reasons. He was later then seen at 8pm roaming around the department's parking lot. The
professors who saw him said that he looks \"too paranoid\" and \"palingon-lingon po siya.\" 
As stated by eye witnesses, he seems to be hiding from something no one knows. The last time 
the department was checked, there was no person around, especially on times like 8-9pm.
He was seen crying at 9:47pm after he 'disappeared.' No active traces has been seen yet.
"
